  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The ULTRA study will assess the difference in average ventricular voltage output for
      pacemaker patients randomized to Automatic Capture feature ON versus patients randomized to
      Automatic Capture feature OFF.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
